# Apex dynamic paths (/api, /.netlify/functions, /d, /i, /brief) are proxied to
# api.ringdrill.app by the workers/apex-proxy/ Worker, NOT here: Cloudflare Pages
# _redirects can only 200-rewrite to local paths, not an external origin. See
# ADR-0039 and DEBT-0011.

# Vanity redirects for people who type these paths from muscle memory.
# 301 so the browser URL updates.
/web                    https://web.ringdrill.app/                            301
/app                    https://web.ringdrill.app/                            301
